everyone Unfortunately there doesnt seem to be a perfect day but how about FridayDec nd Please respond and tell me what you think I have had a few suggestions for a placeChurrascos Americas Ruggles Benjis Sullivansplease send a suggestion Dont say it doesnt matter because majority vote will win and there will be no recount The time will probably be around pm I know the nd is close to Christmas so the th has also been suggestedbut I am afraid not everyone will be in town yet Please send me your thoughts on the day restauraunt and if we should plan something after dinner I cant wait to see everyone and hope all can make it Laura
